      • indexBooleanRoiProperties

        public void indexBooleanRoiProperties(java.lang.String dataset)
        Creates an index for each ROI present in the dataset. ROIs are stored as boolean properties (set to true) on Neuron/Segment nodes and Synapse (PreSyn and PostSyn) nodes.
        Parameters:
        dataset - dataset for load

      • createMetaNodeWithDataModelNode

        public void createMetaNodeWithDataModelNode(java.lang.String dataset,
                                            float dataModelVersion,
                                            double preHPThreshold,
                                            double postHPThreshold,
                                            boolean addConnectionSetRoiInfoAndWeightHP,
                                            java.time.LocalDateTime timeStamp)
        Adds a Meta node and DataModel node to the database (if they do not exist). The Meta node stores summary information for a given dataset. The DataModel node indicates the data model version and links to all Meta nodes in the database with an Is relationship.
        Parameters:
        dataset - dataset name
        dataModelVersion - version of data model
        preHPThreshold - high-precision threshold for presynaptic densities
        postHPThreshold - high-precision threshold for postsynaptic densities
        addConnectionSetRoiInfoAndWeightHP - boolean indicating if ConnectionSet nodes should have roiInfo property and weightHP should be added to ConnectsTo relationships
        timeStamp - time stamp for load

      • addConnectionInfo

        public void addConnectionInfo(java.lang.String dataset,
                              java.util.List<Neuron> neuronList,
                              boolean addConnectionSetRoiInfoAndWeightHP,
                              double preHPThreshold,
                              double postHPThreshold,
                              long neuronThreshold)
        Adds connection information (ConnectsTo relationships, ConnectionSets, weight/weightHP, roiInfo and pre/post counts on Segments, :Neuron label) based on synaptic connections.
        Parameters:
        dataset - dataset name
        neuronList - list of Neuron objects
        addConnectionSetRoiInfoAndWeightHP - boolean indicating if ConnectionSet nodes should have roiInfo property and weightHP should be added to ConnectsTo relationships
        preHPThreshold - high-precision threshold for presynaptic densities
        postHPThreshold - high-precision threshold for postsynaptic densities
        neuronThreshold - Neuron must have greater than or equal to neuronThreshold/5 presynaptic densities or greater than or equal to neuronThreshold postsynaptic densities to be given a :Neuron label

      • addSkeletonNodes

        public void addSkeletonNodes(java.lang.String dataset,
                             java.util.List<Skeleton> skeletonList,
                             java.time.LocalDateTime timeStamp)
        Adds Skeleton and SkelNode nodes to database. Segments are connected to Skeletons via Contains relationships. Skeletons are connected to SkelNodes via Contains relationships. SkelNodes point to their children with LinksTo relationships.
        Parameters:
        dataset - dataset name
        skeletonList - list of Skeleton objects
        timeStamp - time of data load

      • addMetaInfo

        public void addMetaInfo(java.lang.String dataset,
                        MetaInfo metaInfo,
                        java.time.LocalDateTime timeStamp)
        Adds meta information to the Meta node for the provided dataset. Meta information is stored as a MetaInfo object, which is loaded from a json provided during the load.
        Parameters:
        dataset - dataset for load
        metaInfo - MetaInfo object
        timeStamp - time stamp for load
